    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away and spotless. If you're looking for a total gem that needs zero work, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
