      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo represents a peerless example of the A80 chassis. Powered by the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, the sequential twin-turbocharged powertrain delivers linear torque across the rev range, mated to a crisp V160 Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is absolute, featuring a factory-correct limited-slip differential and unmodified suspension kinematics. Every bushing, seal, and fluid line reflects meticulous preventative maintenance. The exterior finish is flawless, preserving the aerodynamic profile and structural rigidity of a true grand tourer. This is an investment-grade specimen for the discerning collector.",
